<lb ed="L" n="0376b04"/>名</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form><term rend="no_nor"><g ref="#CB22150">𪀝</g></term></form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0376b0403" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">于權切音緣同鳶鷙鳥也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
